<http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.3846.3.3>
    bibo:endPage "397" ;
    bibo:issue "3" ;
    bibo:journal "Zootaxa" ;
    bibo:startPage "361" ;
    bibo:volume "3846" ;
    dc:creator "Iniesta, Luiz Felipe Moretti; Ferreira, Rodrigo Lopes" ;
    dc:date "2014" ;
    dc:title "New species of Pseudonannolene Silvestri, 1895 from Brazilian limestone caves with comments on the potential distribution of the genus in South America (Spirostreptida: Pseudonannolenidae)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.250109>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.250110>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.250121>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.250122>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.250111>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.250112> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.250109>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Pseudonannolene leopoldoi sp. n. (holotype, ISLA 4123): a) Anterior region; b) Pre-femoral process; c) Caudal view of gonopod; d) Oral view of gonopod. Scale bar: a) 1 mm; b) 700 µm; c) 300 µm; d) 300 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/250109/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.250110>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Individuals of Pseudonannolene leopoldoi observed feeding on fungi that developed in carcass of grasshopers." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/250110/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.250121>
    dc:description "FIGURE 14. Live specimens: a) Pseudonannolene xavieri sp. n.; b) Pseudonannolene leopoldoi sp. n.; c) Pseudonannolene robsoni sp. n.; d) Pseudonannolene marconii sp. n.; e) Pseudonannolene rosineii sp. n.; f) Pseudonannolene caatinga sp. n.; g) Pseudonannolene taboa sp. n.; h) Pseudonannolene fontanettiae sp. n." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/250121/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.250122>
    dc:description "FIGURE 15. Caves where the specimens were found: a) Paranoá cave (P. rosineii sp. n.); b) Rei do Mato cave (P. erikae sp. n. and P. longisima sp. n.); c) Lapa do Zu cave (P. leopoldoi sp. n.); d) Casa da Pedra cave (P. fontanettiae sp. n.); e) Taboa cave (P. taboa sp. n.); f) Milagrosa cave P. marconii sp. n.); g) Toca dos Ossos cave (P. caatinga sp. n.); h) Lapa do Baio cave (P. xavieri sp. n.); i) Brega cave (P. robsoni sp. n.)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/250122/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.250111>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Pseudonannolene robsoni sp. n. (holotype, ISLA 4080): a) Anterior region; b) Pre-femoral process; c) Caudal view of gonopod; d) Oral view of gonopod. Scale bar: a) 2 mm; b) 500 µm; c) 700 µm; d) 700 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/250111/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.250112>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Grouping of individuals of Pseudonannolene robsoni feeding on rodent feces." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/250112/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

